# Graphs and Statistics

-   [darcs-graph](http://hackage.haskell.org/package/darcs-graph) Render
    graphs of commit activity of a darcs repository
-   [darcsstats](http://vmiklos.hu/project/darcsstats/) Generates a HTML
    page with statistics of author contributions

# Activity Notifications

-   [DarcsMonitor](RelatedSoftware/DarcsMonitor) - will send email to a
    specified recipient about new changes added to a specific darcs
    repository.
-   [darcs-notify](http://porkrind.org/darcs-notify) - sends email about
    patches that are pushed to, pulled to, or unpulled from a specific
    darcs repository.
-   [darcs-patch-watch](RelatedSoftware/DarcsPatchWatch) - a
    [lambdabot](http://www.cse.unsw.edu.au/~dons/lambdabot.html) plugin
    for posting repository changes to an IRC channel.

# Project management / bug tracking
-   [trac-darcs](http://hub.darcs.net/lelit/trac-darcs) - a Darcs
    plugin to [Trac](http://trac.edgewall.org/)
-   [Redmine](http://www.redmine.org/projects/redmine) - a project management web application
-   [ChillProject](https://www.chiliproject.org/projects/chiliproject) - a Redmine fork
-   [darcs-history](RelatedSoftware/DarcsHistory) - tracking patch movement history of a repository

